Nollywood actor, Yul Edochie, on Tuesday, shared a video of the “fun moment” he had with his first wife, May. In the video shared on the actor’s Instagram page, the duo was vibing to a song inside a car. He captioned the video, “Fun moment with my angel. CEO extraordinaire @mayyuledochie.” Watch video below:  The couple has been enmeshed in social media drama following the actor’s second marriage to fellow actress, Judy Austin. After the announcement, Yul’s wife of 17 years called on God’s judgement on the couple and unfollowed her husband on Instagram. Despite the recent video shared by Yul, checks by our correspondent showed that May has not followed her husband again on the social media platform. Copyright PUNCH. All rights reserved. This material, and other digital content on this website, may not be reproduced, published, broadcast, rewritten or redistributed in whole or in part without prior express written permission from PUNCH. Contact: theeditor@punchng.com